	<h1>CBA Brief Coding - Third Year</h1>
	<p>Design and make a project which explores an area of interest to you from the coding course. Your project must:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Be documented in full on your website</li>
		<li>Be completed on time</li>
		<li>Be completed in one of Scratch, CodeArcade, MicroBit or Python</li>
	</ul>
	
	<p>As part of the project you must analyse the brief, produce a "statement of intent" which explains what your project will be and what
	it will look like. </p>
	<p>You must also sketch your design ideas for how this project will appear or create a basic story board. Photos of this should be put on to the Page
	titled design</p>
	<p>Other items that must be produced:</p>
